OL,5, There are serious concerns over the    
OL,6, standards of specialist care being     
OL,7, provided to patients with the most     
OL,8, complex mental health needs, a BBC     
OL,9, investigation has found.               
OL,11,FPatients sent by the NHS to stay in    
OL,12,Fmental health rehabilitation units say 
OL,13,Fthey have been placed in unsafe        
OL,14,Fenvironments, often far from home, with
OL,15,Funtrained staff.                       
OL,17,FExperts say not enough is being done to
OL,18,Fregulate the sector, which costs the   
OL,19,FNHS half a billion pounds a year.      
